title: Welcome to Beautifully updated 3 bed 2 bath Ranch home!!
posting_body: ['E 29th St, This sophisticated and luxurious city retreat with masterful design & modern luxury are uniquely embodied in this 1945 two-story cottage.', 'Love where you live & play in the desirable, well established Swansboro neighborhood & near Places to see, ways to wander & signature experiences, with a mix of the charming, modern, and tried and true.', "Entertain in grand style with sprawling spaces & graced by soaring Ceilings with an elegant open dining room, classic living room with fireplace and a tremendous chef's kitchen that offers premium finishes and fixtures with island.", 'No need to trudge up the stairs with Two spacious bedrooms & full guest bath with ceramic tile on this level.', 'Nicely appointed & Just up the staircase sits the Primary Bedroom with an opulent en-suite, Bedroom 4, the third renovated bath with ceramic tile & flex space for work or play.', 'Other Amenities include renovation to the studs, 1st floor laundry, new roof, new 2 zoned HVAC, new siding & handpicked finishes.', 'Outdoor living is easy in this impressive home with new privacy fencing, patio for grilling, freshly landscaped & much more!', 'Perfect for anyone, perfect for you!', 'Call us today to get in on this GREAT deal…( 8 5 5 ) 6 5 3 - 0 8 5 9']
